                <h3>Success factors</h3>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec finibus elit at facilisis auctor. Orci varius natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.</p>

                <h3>Support offered</h3>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec finibus elit at facilisis auctor. Orci varius natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.</p>

                <p>It’s also important to us that you are committed to equalities and the environment. We’ll want to know about your equalities policy and your environmental policy if we’re interested in your idea.</p>

                <ul>
                    <li><a href="https://www.biglotteryfund.org.uk/about-big/our-approach/equalities">Our equality principles</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/environmental-responsibility-for-charities">Visit gov.uk for more information on environmental responsibility</a></li>
                </ul>

                <p>If you think this fund might be right for you, the first stage is to talk to us.</p>

                <p><a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/strand-2/eligibility" class="btn btn--medium accent--{{ pageAccent }} a--btn">
                    Request a call
                </a></p>
            {% endcall %}

            {% call contentBox(pageAccent) %}
                <h2>Does this not sound like you?</h2>

                <p>Choose one of the following options instead.</p>

                <p><a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/alternative-funding"
                    class="btn btn--medium accent--pink a--btn">
                    We want help getting started with digital
                </a></p>
                <p><a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/strand-1"
                    class="btn btn--medium accent--blue a--btn">
                    We want to use digital to change our core business
                </a></p>
            {% endcall %}
        </div>
    </main>
{% endblock %}
